I"¶E<a href="/assets/Ring/Ring.jpg">
<img src="/assets/Ring/Thumbnails/Ring.jpg" alt="Ring">
</a>
<div class="image-caption">Ring</div>

<p>My wife does not have a wedding band. We‚Äôve been together since 2000, and she‚Äôs never had one. So I‚Äôm going to see if I can make one.</p>

<p>I‚Äôve never made a ring before and I did zero research on how to do this. I just put some thought power in to it and then whacked at some wood.</p>

<p>Here‚Äôs my process‚Ä¶</p>

<!--more-->

